text: The Team 'Aero Kickboxing with Step' category involved four teams representing four countries all based in Europe. Each team went through five performances (1.5 to 2 minutes each) with the totals added up at the end of the event. The gold medal winner was Team Hungary, Team Portugal claimed silver and Team Croatia claimed bronze. ==Results== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Position ! Contestant ! 1 ! 2 ! 3 ! 4 ! 5 !
